trans-unit.target: 如果 <paramref name="patternInterface" /> 為 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.GridItem" />，這個方法會傳回 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer" /> 目前的執行個體，否則會傳回 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TableCell" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer" /> is understood by the end user as interactive or as contributing to the logical structure of the control in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_gui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-gui-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定值，這個值指出與這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TableCell" /> 相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer" /> 會由使用者辨識為互動式，還是做為 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_gui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-gui-md.md)] 中控制項的邏輯結構。
